def drw(date):

    sns.set(
        rc={
            "figure.dpi": 200,
            "ytick.labelsize": 8,
            "xtick.labelsize": 8,
            "figure.figsize": (10, 6),
        }
    )
    sns.set_style("dark")
    plt.xkcd()

    ax = sns.lineplot(data=tcmb_agr_ort_fonlama_faiz.iloc[-date:, 1:], legend=False)
    ax.xaxis.set_major_locator(plt.NullLocator())

    ax.set_ylim(
        tcmb_agr_ort_fonlama_faiz["Toplam Fonlama"][-date:].values.min() * 0.95,
        ax.get_ylim()[1] * 1.1,
    )
    ax.fill_between(
        x=range(0, len(tcmb_agr_ort_fonlama_faiz.iloc[-date:, 0:0])),
        y1=tcmb_agr_ort_fonlama_faiz["Toplam Fonlama"][-date:].values,
        y2=tcmb_agr_ort_fonlama_faiz["Toplam Fonlama"][-date:].values.min(),
        alpha=0.2,
    )

    ax2 = plt.twinx()
    sns.lineplot(
        data=tcmb_agr_ort_fonlama_faiz.iloc[-date:, 0:1], alpha=0.4, legend=False
    )
    ax2.xaxis.set_major_locator(plt.MaxNLocator(10))

    ax3 = plt.table(
        cellText=table.astype(str).values,
        colLabels=table.columns,
        cellLoc="center",
        rowLoc="center",
        bbox=[0.02, 0.62, 0.3, 0.3],
        zorder=3,
        alpha=0.1,
    )
    ax3.auto_set_font_size(False)
    ax3.set_fontsize(6)

    plt.show()
